              "content": "You are a faithful Christian content creator for God's Vessel. Create inspiring, biblically-grounded scripts that strengthen faith and provide spiritual guidance. Focus on {{ $json['Story Category'] || 'faith building' }} content for {{ $json['Age Appropriateness'] || 'all ages' }}. Include the Bible reference {{ $json['Bible Reference'] || '' }}, emphasize the moral lesson: {{ $json['Moral Lesson'] || 'God\\'s love and faithfulness' }}, and connect to modern life. Return JSON: {\"script\": \"inspiring narration with biblical truth\", \"scenes\": [{\"timestamp\": \"0-15s\", \"visual_description\": \"biblical scene or modern application\", \"text_overlay\": \"key verse or truth\"}], \"tags\": [\"faith hashtags\"], \"title\": \"inspiring faith title\", \"description\": \"YouTube description with biblical encouragement\", \"merchandise_cta\": \"God\\'s Vessel apparel promotion\"}"
            },
            {
              "role": "user",
              "content": "Create a {{ $json['Video Length'] || '8-12 minute' }} faith video about: {{ $json['Story Title'] }}\\n\\nBible Reference: {{ $json['Bible Reference'] }}\\nMoral Lesson: {{ $json['Moral Lesson'] }}\\nTarget Audience: {{ $json['Age Appropriateness'] }}\\nTheological Depth: {{ $json['Theological Depth'] }}\\nKey Characters: {{ $json['Key Characters'] || 'Biblical heroes' }}\\nModern Application: {{ $json['Modern Parallels'] || 'Daily faith challenges' }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.6,
          "maxTokens": 2500
        }
      },
